videos.description: Crystal Dangerfield picks the pocket of Antoinette Miller, runs the floor and flips it to Kyla Irwin for an easy lay-in.
videos.headline: Dangerfield steals and Irwin scores

videos.description: Katie Lou Samuelson misses the lay-in, but Naphessa Collier gets the rebound and dishes it to Crystal Dangerfield who knocks down a deep three.
videos.headline: Dangerfield nails deep 3

videos.description: Crystal Dangerfield penetrates the paint, fakes the floater and flips a dime to Naphessa Collier for the bucket.
videos.headline: Dangerfield delivers beautiful dime

videos.description: Megan Walker blocks Nikira Goings, Katie Lou Samuelson gets the rebound and dishes to a running Walker who scores the jumper.
videos.headline: Walker rejects and scores
